    Link: http://lkml.kernel.org/r/20151130215436.GA25996@altlinux.org
    Signed-off-by: Thomas Gleixner <tglx@linutronix.de>

diff --git a/arch/x86/kernel/signal.c b/arch/x86/kernel/signal.c
